1
00:00:08,070 --> 00:00:10,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Which faction do you want to join?</font>

2
00:00:10,820 --> 00:00:13,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Many ladies have recruited me,</font>

3
00:00:13,770 --> 00:00:17,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but it's impossible for 
me to choose just one.</font>

4
00:00:17,850 --> 00:00:18,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Therefore...</font>

5
00:00:18,870 --> 00:00:21,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm going to join all the factions.</font>

6
00:00:21,370 --> 00:00:22,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

7
00:00:22,250 --> 00:00:23,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?</font>

8
00:00:28,210 --> 00:00:30,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And you think you're worth it?</font>

9
00:00:31,630 --> 00:00:32,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Who knows?</font>

10
00:00:36,950 --> 00:00:38,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Say it again.</font>

11
00:00:40,020 --> 00:00:43,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You think you're worthy of joint
faction membership?</font>

12
00:00:43,510 --> 00:00:44,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I do not know.</font>

13
00:00:44,850 --> 00:00:50,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But in order to be someone you wish 
me to be, I shall give it my all!</font>

14
00:00:51,740 --> 00:00:54,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Then please prove your worth.</font>

15
00:00:55,470 --> 00:00:57,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Coming from a man, I'm not...</font>

16
00:00:57,900 --> 00:00:59,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Please, Shilto!</font>

17
00:00:59,220 --> 00:01:02,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He totally changes his reaction 
between men and women.</font>

18
00:01:03,240 --> 00:01:05,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We're going to test your skills.</font>

19
00:01:05,540 --> 00:01:07,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">For you, Miss Shilto,</font>

20
00:01:07,690 --> 00:01:13,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can even pull off four consecutive
all-nighters, which my maid has banned!</font>

21
00:02:44,200 --> 00:02:51,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}THE UNPRECEDENTED TROUBLEMAKER</font>

22
00:02:45,310 --> 00:02:49,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Kunon Gurion's taking on the 
three factions in a magic battle?!</font>

23
00:02:49,020 --> 00:02:51,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He's still new, isn't he?</font>

24
00:02:51,200 --> 00:02:53,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why make a trainee like that do this?</font>

25
00:02:53,410 --> 00:02:57,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But apparently this guy is the 
student of Zeonly Finroll.</font>

26
00:02:57,280 --> 00:02:59,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?! He's Master Zeonly's student?!</font>

27
00:02:59,980 --> 00:03:01,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I've got to see it!</font>

28
00:03:01,530 --> 00:03:04,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, I simply must see it!</font>

29
00:03:11,970 --> 00:03:14,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I hope Kunon's going to be okay.</font>

30
00:03:14,570 --> 00:03:17,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If he gets hurt, Reyes 
can heal him, right?</font>

31
00:03:17,630 --> 00:03:20,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He brought it on himself, 
but I guess I shall.</font>

32
00:03:26,620 --> 00:03:27,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll go, too.</font>

33
00:03:27,980 --> 00:03:30,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm gonna beat him up!</font>

34
00:03:32,930 --> 00:03:37,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Causing such an uproar is what I'd 
expect from the student on Zeon.</font>

35
00:03:38,510 --> 00:03:41,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll do my best to meet your 
expectations, Professor Sayfie.</font>

36
00:03:42,410 --> 00:03:45,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If I win, how about we get a delicious
parfait at a café as a reward?</font>

37
00:03:46,230 --> 00:03:48,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Do not hit on your professor.</font>

38
00:03:49,670 --> 00:03:50,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh?</font>

39
00:03:50,850 --> 00:03:52,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's beautiful. Made of magic silver?</font>

40
00:03:53,130 --> 00:03:55,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes. It's my lucky charm.</font>

41
00:04:15,880 --> 00:04:18,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Everyone's so intense.</font>

42
00:04:18,250 --> 00:04:21,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They're the top sorcerers 
in the advanced class.</font>

43
00:04:21,980 --> 00:04:22,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Especially...</font>

44
00:04:23,180 --> 00:04:24,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sandra. She's here, too.</font>

45
00:04:25,220 --> 00:04:27,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If she's in this, then I'm worried 
about the collateral damage.</font>

46
00:04:28,300 --> 00:04:29,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Collateral?</font>

47
00:04:29,390 --> 00:04:32,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She's good at bold moves 
but sucks at control.</font>

48
00:04:32,420 --> 00:04:34,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She'll mow down everyone in sight.</font>

49
00:04:34,200 --> 00:04:35,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Really?</font>

50
00:04:35,880 --> 00:04:39,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Somehow, I can't imagine 
that Kunon would lose.</font>

51
00:04:39,460 --> 00:04:40,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">True.</font>

52
00:04:40,660 --> 00:04:42,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I kind of get that.</font>

53
00:04:51,940 --> 00:04:55,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is a quasi-barrier to 
guard against attacking spells.</font>

54
00:04:55,740 --> 00:05:00,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The match is over when this magic 
circle is broken or someone yields.</font>

55
00:05:01,160 --> 00:05:02,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Who wants to go first?</font>

56
00:05:03,100 --> 00:05:04,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll go!</font>

57
00:05:04,200 --> 00:05:06,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why do you get to decide that?</font>

58
00:05:06,260 --> 00:05:07,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm going first.</font>

59
00:05:07,560 --> 00:05:09,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Going by the order determined 
by the representatives,</font>

60
00:05:09,730 --> 00:05:11,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ability should go first.</font>

61
00:05:11,150 --> 00:05:13,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't think that matters anymore.</font>

62
00:05:13,450 --> 00:05:15,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's right! Stay out of this, uggo!</font>

63
00:05:15,960 --> 00:05:17,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm not ugly.</font>

64
00:05:18,410 --> 00:05:23,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Please don't fight over me, 
my beautiful fairies and the other one.</font>

65
00:05:23,210 --> 00:05:25,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're the cause of all this!</font>

66
00:05:25,720 --> 00:05:27,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you referring to 
me as "the other one"?!</font>

67
00:05:28,200 --> 00:05:30,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can take you all on at once, ladies.</font>

68
00:05:30,600 --> 00:05:31,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

69
00:05:31,240 --> 00:05:31,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?</font>

70
00:05:31,870 --> 00:05:32,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Say what?</font>

71
00:05:32,290 --> 00:05:33,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Come again?</font>

72
00:05:33,910 --> 00:05:37,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm confident I can win regardless 
of how many come at me.</font>

73
00:05:37,450 --> 00:05:39,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If it's the first time.</font>

74
00:05:39,230 --> 00:05:40,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?</font>

75
00:05:40,300 --> 00:05:41,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Did he just say all at once?</font>

76
00:05:41,770 --> 00:05:42,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's crazy talk.</font>

77
00:05:42,770 --> 00:05:44,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Did he say four of them at once?</font>

78
00:05:45,210 --> 00:05:47,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What is Kunon thinking?</font>

79
00:05:47,800 --> 00:05:50,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">As long as he doesn't die,
 it's not a problem.</font>

80
00:05:50,310 --> 00:05:52,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can heal him.</font>

81
00:05:56,710 --> 00:05:59,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Here's the roster of 
the factions this year.</font>

82
00:05:59,590 --> 00:06:02,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There may be some changes later.</font>

83
00:06:04,420 --> 00:06:05,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's the matter?</font>

84
00:06:06,600 --> 00:06:11,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Actually, a first-year student seems 
to be causing a commotion about this.</font>

85
00:06:13,830 --> 00:06:16,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That brat, huh?</font>

86
00:06:17,860 --> 00:06:19,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let us begin.</font>

87
00:06:19,130 --> 00:06:20,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm excited!</font>

88
00:06:22,190 --> 00:06:24,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He's so cocky.</font>

89
00:06:24,730 --> 00:06:26,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you really sure?</font>

90
00:06:26,740 --> 00:06:27,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes!</font>

91
00:06:29,220 --> 00:06:31,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Cocky, cocky, cocky!</font>

92
00:06:31,490 --> 00:06:34,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You shouldn't provoke them, Kunon.</font>

93
00:06:34,980 --> 00:06:37,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How is he planning to win?</font>

94
00:06:37,730 --> 00:06:41,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What? He has to break 
that magic circle, right?</font>

95
00:06:41,500 --> 00:06:45,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't believe he's 
learned any attack spells.</font>

96
00:06:46,380 --> 00:06:47,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh!</font>

97
00:06:53,950 --> 00:06:55,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Please begin!</font>

98
00:06:59,180 --> 00:07:02,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>He's only got two 
elementary spells, right?</i></font>

99
00:07:02,400 --> 00:07:06,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>He's Zeonly's student, huh? Yikes.</i></font>

100
00:07:06,870 --> 00:07:09,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>What is he up to?</i></font>

101
00:07:09,370 --> 00:07:11,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I guess I'll wait and see.</i></font>

102
00:07:14,310 --> 00:07:15,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A-ori.</font>

103
00:07:19,080 --> 00:07:21,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>And it's a very basic one.</i></font>

104
00:07:21,890 --> 00:07:22,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Multiply.</font>

105
00:07:28,150 --> 00:07:28,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Multiply.</font>

106
00:07:33,800 --> 00:07:34,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Multiply.</font>

107
00:07:38,150 --> 00:07:39,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Multiply.</font>

108
00:07:39,500 --> 00:07:40,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Multiply.</font>

109
00:07:40,610 --> 00:07:41,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Multiply.</font>

110
00:07:41,900 --> 00:07:42,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Multiply.</font>

111
00:07:43,090 --> 00:07:43,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Color.</font>

112
00:07:48,190 --> 00:07:49,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's...</font>

113
00:07:49,240 --> 00:07:52,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The red fog he used 
against Professor Soff.</font>

114
00:08:03,310 --> 00:08:04,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wait, what?</font>

115
00:08:04,730 --> 00:08:06,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is A-ori, too?</font>

116
00:08:07,090 --> 00:08:09,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's clinging to me.</font>

117
00:08:09,210 --> 00:08:14,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, don't get my clothes dirty! 
I love this outfit!</font>

118
00:08:14,470 --> 00:08:16,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Calm down! It's just fog!</font>

119
00:08:17,850 --> 00:08:20,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>He's obscuring our sight so he can attack?</i></font>

120
00:08:28,990 --> 00:08:30,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What the heck is this?</font>

121
00:08:33,580 --> 00:08:36,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Coloring it must be a bluff.</i></font>

122
00:08:36,520 --> 00:08:39,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>It's a basic water spell, A-ori.</i></font>

123
00:08:39,370 --> 00:08:41,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>It's only water.</i></font>

124
00:08:44,470 --> 00:08:45,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I was wrong!</i></font>

125
00:08:45,370 --> 00:08:48,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's my turn now! Just you watch...</font>

126
00:08:54,850 --> 00:08:56,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ew, I don't like this.</font>

127
00:08:57,040 --> 00:08:59,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is this... slime?</font>

128
00:09:06,400 --> 00:09:08,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You got me! I yield!</font>

129
00:09:11,270 --> 00:09:14,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We lose, Kunon Gurion.</font>

130
00:09:15,710 --> 00:09:16,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okay.</font>

131
00:09:16,660 --> 00:09:18,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh? It's over?</font>

132
00:09:18,710 --> 00:09:20,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Just because it rained?</font>

133
00:09:21,190 --> 00:09:24,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why didn't they counterattack?</font>

134
00:09:24,150 --> 00:09:27,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They lost on purpose 
because they wanted Kunon?</font>

135
00:09:27,640 --> 00:09:29,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't think so.</font>

136
00:09:29,290 --> 00:09:33,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">In the name of their factions, 
they wouldn't dare lose to a first-year.</font>

137
00:09:33,570 --> 00:09:34,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That magic circle...</font>

138
00:09:35,670 --> 00:09:38,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why use the quasi-barrier?</font>

139
00:09:38,530 --> 00:09:42,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The rain obviously passed 
through the barrier.</font>

140
00:09:46,870 --> 00:09:49,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I passed the test, didn't I?</font>

141
00:09:58,460 --> 00:10:00,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You didn't hold back, did you?</font>

142
00:10:00,070 --> 00:10:01,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Who's going to clean this up?</font>

143
00:10:01,990 --> 00:10:03,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Have no fear.</font>

144
00:10:03,690 --> 00:10:05,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It'll disappear when I release it.</font>

145
00:10:12,070 --> 00:10:15,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you all right, my beautiful mermaids?</font>

146
00:10:15,210 --> 00:10:16,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A-ori.</font>

147
00:10:17,130 --> 00:10:19,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Here's my apology for making you cold.</font>

148
00:10:20,020 --> 00:10:22,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Think of this as the warmth of my heart.</font>

149
00:10:22,600 --> 00:10:24,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's warm?</font>

150
00:10:27,670 --> 00:10:28,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Here you go.</font>

151
00:10:28,730 --> 00:10:29,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Get lost!</font>

152
00:10:34,050 --> 00:10:35,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Would you like one?</font>

153
00:10:43,890 --> 00:10:47,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So what was that red rain, exactly?</font>

154
00:10:47,840 --> 00:10:50,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, who knows?</font>

155
00:10:52,630 --> 00:10:53,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What did you do?</font>

156
00:10:53,910 --> 00:10:55,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's sticky water!</font>

157
00:10:55,680 --> 00:10:59,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You know, it's like slime rain.</font>

158
00:10:59,320 --> 00:11:01,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, the color is irrelevant.</font>

159
00:11:01,670 --> 00:11:03,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It just needed to be distinguishable.</font>

160
00:11:04,040 --> 00:11:07,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If you're showered with it,
 a counterattack is out of question.</font>

161
00:11:08,260 --> 00:11:10,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It gets in your mouth, 
so you can't chant a spell.</font>

162
00:11:10,510 --> 00:11:11,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let alone breathe...</font>

163
00:11:12,060 --> 00:11:16,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So Sandra and the others 
were right to admit defeat.</font>

164
00:11:18,760 --> 00:11:22,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Then why didn't that magic 
circle repel your attack?</font>

165
00:11:23,340 --> 00:11:28,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What I used was not an
 attack spell, but an elementary A-ori.</font>

166
00:11:29,250 --> 00:11:32,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The amount of magical 
power used was too small?</font>

167
00:11:32,590 --> 00:11:36,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So it didn't recognize it as
 an attack, and it let it through.</font>

168
00:11:37,100 --> 00:11:40,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You knew the properties
 of the magic circle?</font>

169
00:11:40,210 --> 00:11:46,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes. I've done magic battles with that 
magic circle many times with my master.</font>

170
00:11:47,290 --> 00:11:49,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">With Zeonly?!</font>

171
00:11:51,210 --> 00:11:52,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No need to hold back.</font>

172
00:11:53,340 --> 00:11:55,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hit me with everything you've got.</font>

173
00:11:55,710 --> 00:11:58,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll teach you the depth of earth magic.</font>

174
00:11:59,360 --> 00:12:01,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okay, I'll try!</font>

175
00:12:01,250 --> 00:12:02,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">All right, bring it!</font>

176
00:12:13,110 --> 00:12:15,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>The</i> Zeonly...</font>

177
00:12:15,000 --> 00:12:16,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">...lost?</font>

178
00:12:16,100 --> 00:12:18,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is that true?</font>

179
00:12:18,590 --> 00:12:20,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I cannot lie to you.</font>

180
00:12:21,250 --> 00:12:23,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I only won the first battle,</font>

181
00:12:23,820 --> 00:12:27,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and after the second time, he'd hit me
 preemptively and I kept losing.</font>

182
00:12:27,780 --> 00:12:30,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So, if you wait and see, you lose.</font>

183
00:12:30,900 --> 00:12:32,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's nastier than I thought.</font>

184
00:12:32,770 --> 00:12:35,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No one can beat you in the first battle.</font>

185
00:12:35,990 --> 00:12:38,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So that's what you meant.</font>

186
00:12:41,310 --> 00:12:43,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We'll allow your joint membership.</font>

187
00:12:43,400 --> 00:12:51,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes! Now I can spend my school life 
with you without anyone interfering.</font>

188
00:12:51,330 --> 00:12:54,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Just thinking about that makes 
my heart soar until dawn!</font>

189
00:12:56,840 --> 00:13:00,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm pretty sure three self-nominated
 joint memberships is unheard of.</font>

190
00:13:01,140 --> 00:13:04,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We've got someone truly out of the box.</font>

191
00:13:10,680 --> 00:13:12,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Before joining the factions,</font>

192
00:13:12,350 --> 00:13:16,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">you should talk to the seniors
you embarrassed in front of everyone.</font>

193
00:13:16,060 --> 00:13:21,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes. As a gentleman, I'd love to 
get to know those three ladies.</font>

194
00:13:21,300 --> 00:13:22,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And another person.</font>

195
00:13:22,480 --> 00:13:24,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You mean Cassis?</font>

196
00:13:24,550 --> 00:13:27,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'd happily invite ladies any day, but...</font>

197
00:13:28,250 --> 00:13:29,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, the thing is...</font>

198
00:13:36,280 --> 00:13:39,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The heart... of a maiden?</font>

199
00:13:46,980 --> 00:13:49,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The heart of a maiden.</font>

200
00:13:49,150 --> 00:13:51,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The heart of a maiden.</font>

201
00:13:51,490 --> 00:13:55,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Who knew there was a man... 
no, a woman like that?</font>

202
00:13:57,530 --> 00:13:59,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, there you are, Kunon!</font>

203
00:14:01,110 --> 00:14:02,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What happened after that?</font>

204
00:14:02,680 --> 00:14:04,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What was that red rain?</font>

205
00:14:04,670 --> 00:14:07,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The whole school is talking about it.</font>

206
00:14:07,830 --> 00:14:10,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Did you solve the issue 
with the factions?</font>

207
00:14:12,620 --> 00:14:14,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They approved joint membership?!</font>

208
00:14:14,420 --> 00:14:16,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's amazing, Kunon!</font>

209
00:14:16,870 --> 00:14:18,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I still have a long way to go.</font>

210
00:14:20,180 --> 00:14:24,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I am so ashamed of my 
ungentlemanly behavior.</font>

211
00:14:28,540 --> 00:14:31,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can't look Her Highness in the eye.</font>

212
00:14:41,540 --> 00:14:43,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, Mirika!</font>

213
00:14:43,150 --> 00:14:45,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you ready?</font>

214
00:14:45,140 --> 00:14:46,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You'd better be.</font>

215
00:14:46,810 --> 00:14:51,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I told you I'd be fine 
by myself, Brother Lyle.</font>

216
00:14:51,280 --> 00:14:53,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's a big day for the vice captain.</font>

217
00:14:53,470 --> 00:14:56,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's only natural I watch over 
it as the captain, right?</font>

218
00:14:58,430 --> 00:15:00,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>How are you, Kunon?</i></font>

219
00:15:01,530 --> 00:15:04,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Today, I'm finally taking the exam 
for the knighthood department</i></font>

220
00:15:04,470 --> 00:15:05,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>at the senior school for nobles.</i></font>

221
00:15:06,170 --> 00:15:08,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Next! Mirika Hughlia!</font>

222
00:15:08,420 --> 00:15:09,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes!</font>

223
00:15:21,070 --> 00:15:21,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Begin!</font>

224
00:15:46,420 --> 00:15:49,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There you go. That's my vice captain.</font>

225
00:15:49,390 --> 00:15:50,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Match over!</font>

226
00:15:50,570 --> 00:15:52,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Mirika Hughlia!</font>

227
00:15:53,210 --> 00:15:56,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I will become a woman worthy of you.</i></font>

228
00:15:56,570 --> 00:16:00,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>So please do your best 
at the magic school.</i></font>

229
00:16:04,610 --> 00:16:05,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?</font>

230
00:16:06,210 --> 00:16:08,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Her Highness, in the 
knighthood department?</font>

231
00:16:08,580 --> 00:16:12,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Master Kunon! It's getting cold,
 so let's head inside.</font>

232
00:16:15,630 --> 00:16:16,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Master Kunon?</font>

233
00:16:17,420 --> 00:16:18,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's up?</font>

234
00:16:18,420 --> 00:16:20,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's time for dinner.</font>

235
00:16:20,010 --> 00:16:21,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Already?</font>

236
00:16:22,820 --> 00:16:25,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Shall I bring you a fresh warm one?</font>

237
00:16:25,450 --> 00:16:26,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh.</font>

238
00:16:26,350 --> 00:16:27,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No, it's fine.</font>

239
00:16:28,090 --> 00:16:30,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll drink it at night, 
so take it to my room.</font>

240
00:16:30,680 --> 00:16:34,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's the milk tea you 
make for me with love.</font>

241
00:16:34,130 --> 00:16:35,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's right.</font>

242
00:16:35,550 --> 00:16:37,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There's no tea in it, though.</font>

243
00:16:37,940 --> 00:16:41,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Rinko. Do you ever cut 
yourself with a knife?</font>

244
00:16:41,480 --> 00:16:44,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm a pro, so I don't.</font>

245
00:16:44,310 --> 00:16:46,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I see. Please be careful.</font>

246
00:16:46,900 --> 00:16:49,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is everything okay?</font>

247
00:16:49,080 --> 00:16:51,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're awfully kind today, Master Kunon.</font>

248
00:16:51,650 --> 00:16:55,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm always kind,
 because I'm a gentleman.</font>

249
00:17:15,720 --> 00:17:18,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>My dear fiancée.</i></font>

250
00:17:18,440 --> 00:17:20,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>How are you?</i></font>

251
00:17:21,290 --> 00:17:24,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I suppose I should congratulate you on 
enrolling in the knighthood department</i></font>

252
00:17:25,670 --> 00:17:27,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>at the senior school for nobles.</i></font>

253
00:17:29,270 --> 00:17:32,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>But I'm very worried.</i></font>

254
00:17:32,490 --> 00:17:35,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>You must be training hard every day, 
like your life depends on it.</i></font>

255
00:17:36,310 --> 00:17:38,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>There may be times when you get hurt.</i></font>

256
00:17:39,080 --> 00:17:44,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I want to support you and cheer for you, 
but I do not wish to see you suffer.</i></font>

257
00:17:47,220 --> 00:17:49,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, not that I can really see.</font>

258
00:18:17,470 --> 00:18:22,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Please, please, do not 
push yourself too hard.</i></font>

259
00:18:23,400 --> 00:18:24,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I will write to you.</i></font>

260
00:18:25,140 --> 00:18:27,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Again and again, many times.</i></font>

261
00:18:28,590 --> 00:18:30,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Please don't forget about me.</i></font>

262
00:18:31,320 --> 00:18:35,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Not a day goes by when 
I don't think about you.</i></font>

263
00:18:43,990 --> 00:18:49,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Your Kunon Gurion, with eternal love.</i></font>

264
00:20:30,270 --> 00:20:33,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He's thinking of me so much.</font>

265
00:20:34,430 --> 00:20:35,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm fine!</font>

266
00:20:35,970 --> 00:20:40,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I've grown so strong that even 
a bear can't scare me away!</font>

267
00:20:40,020 --> 00:20:42,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">When you come back, you'll be surprised.</font>

268
00:20:43,340 --> 00:20:45,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How could I forget about you?</font>

269
00:20:45,100 --> 00:20:49,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm always thinking about you, too.</font>

270
00:20:49,060 --> 00:20:52,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">"With eternal love," oh, my!</font>

271
00:20:55,220 --> 00:21:02,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">"P.S., I've made a few dozen 
more female friends at school."</font>

272
00:21:02,170 --> 00:21:04,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh? Isn't that a lot?!</font>

273
00:21:05,420 --> 00:21:10,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">"I've encountered a mysterious 
lady with the heart of a maiden."</font>

274
00:21:10,380 --> 00:21:12,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">"I intend to learn about more ladies</font>

275
00:21:12,420 --> 00:21:17,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and become a gentleman who 
is worthy of Your Highness."</font>

276
00:21:17,740 --> 00:21:23,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">K-Kunon! You don't have to 
work too hard on that front!</font>

277
00:21:23,630 --> 00:21:27,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, good morning, sea birds 
playing in the shallows.</font>

278
00:21:28,130 --> 00:21:32,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I just know that I was 
born to heal your hearts.</font>

279
00:21:32,870 --> 00:21:35,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, Kunon!</font>

280
00:21:35,130 --> 00:21:36,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Cassis!</font>

281
00:21:36,980 --> 00:21:40,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">As an apology for my rude behavior,
I'd like to invite you to lunch,</font>

282
00:21:40,840 --> 00:21:45,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and the gentleman in me is jumping
as if to dance so early in the morning.</font>

283
00:21:45,550 --> 00:21:48,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Please accept my invitation.</font>

284
00:21:48,380 --> 00:21:49,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Shut up!</font>

285
00:21:49,340 --> 00:21:51,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm the type to hold grudge.</font>

286
00:21:51,230 --> 00:21:53,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I only came because the 
representative told me to!</font>

287
00:21:53,700 --> 00:21:55,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Kunon!</font>

288
00:21:55,500 --> 00:21:59,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Mr. Bael wants you to join him 
in developing a magic tool.</font>

289
00:22:00,020 --> 00:22:01,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wonderful!</font>

290
00:22:01,400 --> 00:22:05,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I will dedicate the knowledge of magic 
tools I learned from my master to you!</font>

291
00:22:05,840 --> 00:22:08,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, now! I was here first!</font>

292
00:22:08,370 --> 00:22:09,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Get lost, you uggo!</font>

293
00:22:09,640 --> 00:22:11,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm not ugly!</font>

294
00:22:11,600 --> 00:22:16,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">As an earth sorcerer, 
I'm interested in Zeonly's knowledge.</font>

295
00:22:16,760 --> 00:22:18,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Will you share it with me as well?</font>

296
00:22:18,910 --> 00:22:20,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, Kunon!</font>

297
00:22:20,230 --> 00:22:22,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Fight me one more time!</font>

298
00:22:22,890 --> 00:22:25,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm not going to lose this time!</font>

299
00:22:25,230 --> 00:22:27,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, shut it, shut it!</font>

300
00:22:27,740 --> 00:22:28,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?!</font>

301
00:22:28,820 --> 00:22:30,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ugly mugs, you all need to get lost!</font>

302
00:22:31,430 --> 00:22:33,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What a mess...</font>

303
00:22:33,740 --> 00:22:36,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's impossible to join 
three factions, isn't it?</font>

304
00:22:39,620 --> 00:22:43,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm going to make pills of shi-shilla.</font>

305
00:22:43,790 --> 00:22:45,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Do you want to write a report on it?</font>

306
00:22:45,990 --> 00:22:48,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Of course I do, Miss Reyes!</font>

307
00:22:51,320 --> 00:22:55,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It seems Kunon joined all three factions.</font>

308
00:22:55,960 --> 00:22:57,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's unprecedented.</font>

309
00:22:58,200 --> 00:23:01,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The first troublemaker since Zeonly.</font>

310
00:23:01,850 --> 00:23:04,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I highly welcome it.</font>

311
00:23:06,660 --> 00:23:10,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So, I'm going on a search for a 
shipwreck with the representative.</font>

312
00:23:10,060 --> 00:23:11,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You interested?</font>

313
00:23:12,140 --> 00:23:13,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A shipwreck?!</font>

314
00:23:13,640 --> 00:23:15,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I would love to come along!</font>

315
00:23:16,790 --> 00:23:19,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Weigh anchor! Set sail!</font>

316
00:23:33,950 --> 00:23:36,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can't suppress my curiosity!</font>

